This work was packaged for Debian by:

    OTB Team <contact@orfeo-toolbox.org> on Thu, 14 Oct 2010 16:22:17 +0200

It was downloaded from <http://hg.orfeo-toolbox.org/>, using command:

    hg clone -r <version> http://hg.orfeo-toolbox.org/OTB

The source tarball is an aggregate of several different works in which the
main one, developed by the CNES (Centre National d'Etudes Spatiales), is
Orfeo-Toolbox (OTB). Other works include ITK, VTK, VXL, FLTK, GDAL, OSSIM,
LibSVM, BGL, TinyXML, OpenJPEG, OpenThreads, muParser, LibKML, LibSIFT,
libLAS, kNN Segmentation Library, GAlib, Expat, ConfigFile, Insight Journal
Publications, dxflib.

